    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-special\">black-market modification</span> for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Plasma Launcher</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Potential upgrades include: Explosion <span class=\"name name-stellar\">damage</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">radius</span>, as well as increasing the maximum number of pre-explosion <span class=\"name name-stellar\">bounces</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一项<span class=\"name name-special\">黑市改装</span>，适用于<span class=\"name name-technology\">等离子发射器</span>。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>开始<VAL_ON>安装升级<>。<br><br>该模块功能灵活，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能提升爆炸<span class=\"name name-stellar\">伤害</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">范围</span>，同时增加爆炸前的最大<span class=\"name name-stellar\">弹跳次数</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">電漿發射器</span>的<span class=\"name name-special\">黑市改造</span>。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此模組富有彈性，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能強化的項目包括：爆炸的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">傷害值</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">半徑</span>，同時增加爆炸前<span class=\"name name-stellar\">反彈</span>的最大次數。"
